  "about_item": [
    "Material - Dog vests made of 95% polyester 5% spande, soft lightweight breathable and more flexible, anxiety vests fasten with velcro closure. easy to put on/off, It is also elastic, which allows continuous mild pressure, relieving stress as well as anxiety. wearing this anxiety shirt is just like having the owner hugging it.",
    "Adjustable Design for A Snug Fit - Dog anxiety vests needs to fit your dog tightly thats will be calming and soothing for your pet, our dog vests design with double compression, adjustable stretching belting wrap dogs body, at the same time, straps that stick well and stay in place to provide constant pressure,according to different body shapes adjustment size , dont worry size issue.",
    "Anti Anxiety Jacket for Large Small Medium Dogs - our dog anxiety vest is a wearable vest-like garment that wraps around your dog’s body like a warm hug that pressure on the torso creates a calming effec，It has helped with her fear and anxiety when thunder or storms are near, suit for thunderstorms,Fireworks,Thunder, Travel, Separation,loud noises, etc it will keep your dog mentally in a safe space.",
    "How Does It Work - Anti anxiety vests are just like harnesses for your dog that help to protect him from getting too hot or cold while he is left alone. They give your dog his own little barrier to protect him from the world. you need to put it on and spend some time with your pet before leaving alone. this Jacket as a constant tight hug. Even in situations where they are prone to stress, dogs may feel more relaxed when wearing dog anxiety vests.",
    "Warranty - This anxiety jacket can be worn in any situation, it can be clean by machine or hand, easy to carry,perfect for your boy girl dog, Note: please refer to the size chart for selection. we stand by our high-quality products.Of course, if you have any problem with our dog clothes for large dogs, please feel free to contact us."
  ],
