        "title": "Soft material,works well",
        "text": "Bought a Large for our 50lb Pittie who trembles and hides when a storm is coming. We had severe weather warnings yesterday so I wrapped him up in it. There are no uncomfortable or rigid seams that dig into his leg pit areas. He STAYED out of the closet and from behind the couch and laid in the floor and gnawed on a nylo bone! I couldn't believe it! He eventually did go behind the couch when we had a loud lightening strike, but overall i feel it helped Rambo and reduced his anxiety. The material is soft and light but wraps securely with strong velcro.",
